OL,7,FThe film has been blocked by the
OL,8,FCentral Board of Film Certification
OL,9,F(CBFC), a government body in India
OL,10,Fwhich approves cinematic releases.
OL,12,FThe move is believed to be over the
OL,13,Ffilm's content, which explores
OL,14,Fviolence in the Indian police force,
OL,15,Fmisogyny and Islamophobia.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
