OL,7,FIt is set in a fictional town in
OL,8,Fnorthern India, centred on a
OL,9,Fhousewife, whose police-officer
OL,10,Fhusband recently dies. "In India, it's
OL,11,Fa real government scheme called
OL,12,F'appointment by compassionate
OL,13,Fgrounds', were she is able to inherit
OL,14,Fhis actual job after he dies," Ms Suri
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"So this a film about a housewife, now
OL,18,Fa widow, who becomes a cop, and it's
OL,19,Fabout her learning about negotiating
OL,20,Fthe power that the uniform brings her."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
