OL,7,FThe film was critically well received,
OL,8,Fafter making its debut at Cannes film
OL,9,Ffestival. Following this, it was also
OL,10,Fthe UK's entry for the Oscars'
OL,11,Finternational feature category, and
OL,12,Fwent on to be nominated for a BAFTA
OL,13,Ffor best debut feature this year.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
