OL,7,FMs Suri, who is from Darlington, said:
OL,8,F"It's just been very exciting to bring
OL,9,Fit to audiences because that's what
OL,10,Fthe awards and BAFTA's, and we were
OL,11,FOscar shortlisted, all of that is
OL,12,Fabout bringing you one step closer to
OL,13,Fan audience, more theatres, and more
OL,14,Fpeople hear about it," she said.
OL,16,FDespite the complementary reviews all
OL,17,Faround the world, the film is still
OL,18,Fbeing blocked from being released in
OL,19,FIndia.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
