OL,7,F"I think its very frustrating," she
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,F"I wanted this film to be a true
OL,11,Fcrossover film that would work equally
OL,12,Fas well for foreign audiences, and
OL,13,Fequally as well for an Indian
OL,14,Faudience. And there's been great
OL,15,Fappetite for the film to be shown in
OL,16,FIndia, but it has been held by the
OL,17,Fcensor board currently.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
