OL,5,Cban
OL,7,F"It is a difficult situation to be in
OL,8,Fbecause you want to keep the integrity
OL,9,Fof the film, but you also want your
OL,10,Ffilm to be seen also by the people you
OL,11,Falso made it for."
OL,13,FThe director says that the CBFC have
OL,14,Fasked for certain parts of Santosh to
OL,15,Fbe cut.
OL,17,F"There were certain cuts that were
OL,18,Fdemanded, so it's about seeing if it
OL,19,Fcan be done without damaging the film.
OL,20,FAnd it's quite a challenge."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
