OL,5,Cban
OL,7,FShe went on to continue that she is
OL,8,Fkeeping to fight to have her film
OL,9,Favailable for audiences in India.
OL,11,F"I don't want to give up on the idea
OL,12,Fthat I won't be able to show in India.
OL,14,F"I don't know quite yet, but I don't
OL,15,Fwant to close any doors. It's
OL,16,Fimportant to me that it does show."
OL,18,FITV Tyne Tees have reached out to CBFC
OL,19,Ffor a comment, but they have not
OL,20,Fresponded.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
